Package org.jsweet.transpiler

Enum Class JSweetProblem

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<JSweetProblem>
org.jsweet.transpiler.JSweetProblem
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<JSweetProblem>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum JSweetProblem extends Enum<JSweetProblem>
This enumeration holds all the possible JSweet transpilation problems (warnings and errors) and the associated messages.
Author:
Renaud Pawlak
